unction is advisable.', 'Synergism', 'The use of naltrexone with other potentially hepatotoxic agents should be avoided whenever possible (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/61308/', '', 'Codeine, Oxymorphone, Tapentadol, Meperidine, Butorphanol, Hydromorphone, Dezocine, Opium, Ibuprofen, Pentazocine, Acetylsalicylic acid, More', 'Dabrafenib, Asciminib, Acalabrutinib, Dacomitinib, Pacritinib, Avapritinib, Selumetinib, Vandetanib, Ibrutinib, Tivozanib, Zanubrutinib, More', 1767369485);
