lowed before the pazopanib dosage is adjusted upward.', 'Metabolism', 'Concomitant use of pazopanib with potent CYP450 3A4 inhibitors should generally be avoided.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/61349/', '', 'Trametinib, Nintedanib, Ceritinib, Afatinib, Dacomitinib, Tivozanib, Alectinib', 'Regorafenib, Copanlisib, Abemaciclib, Erlotinib, Ponatinib, Neratinib, Erdafitinib, Trametinib, Nintedanib, Afatinib, Dacomitinib, More', 1767369485);
